{"aid": "ing5wkxw9zc4l0", "result": {"folders": ["lecture17"], "unique_views": 27, "no_answer": 0, "change_log": [{"data": "infn1nm35pq3rf", "anon": "no", "when": "2016-04-25T06:44:08Z", "uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "data": "infqlemysal11f", "when": "2016-04-25T08:23:28Z", "to": "infn1nm0fu43re", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}], "upvote_ids": [], "id": "infn1nm0fu43re", "bookmarked": 4, "no_answer_followup": 0, "i_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "children": [{"folders": [], "is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2016-04-25T08:23:28Z", "config": {}, "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_order": 2, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "id": "infqlemwmu111e", "history": [{"content": "<p>当使用自旋锁进行临界区访问控制时&#xff0c;并不能保证FIFO的。在Linux等通用操作系统&#xff0c;等待队列也会由于内核可能调整队列顺序而不能保证是FIFO的。于是&#xff0c;会出现饥饿。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>通常锁是内核同步机制&#xff0c;并没有提供相关的系统调用给用户态进程使用&#xff1b;而信号量通常用于用户态&#xff0c;它是基于内核同步机制实现。</p>", "anon": "no", "subject": "", "uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "created": "2016-04-25T08:23:28Z"}]}], "request_instructor_me": false, "nr": 832, "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "status": "active", "tags": ["lecture17", "student"], "num_favorites": 0, "bucket_name": "Today", "q_edits": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor": 0, "created": "2016-04-25T06:44:08Z", "is_tag_good": false, "type": "question", "s_edits": [], "my_favorite": false, "default_anonymity": "no", "t": 1461598324483, "tag_good": [], "tag_good_arr": [], "history": [{"content": "<p>如果原子锁的等待队列也是FIFO的话&#xff0c;这样除了可用资源的限制&#xff0c;跟信号量有什么区别呢&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>为什么MOOC上说原子锁会饥饿&#xff1f;</p>", "anon": "no", "subject": "为什么原子锁会导致饥饿&#xff1f;", "uid": "i0b2fq3ezjw50r", "created": "2016-04-25T06:44:08Z"}]}, "error": null}